{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Project/blog/2/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Tinnia Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b1f29ad8-1b2c-52ce-a0d3-e1ee968e0ca5","excerpt":"2. CSS  오늘은 CSS에 대해 배웠다.   먼저, html은 쉽게 배울 수 있지만, 가장 중요한 기초가 된다. 그리고, CSS는 HTML이 WEB의 정보에 집중할 수 있게, 디자인적 요소를 맡고 있다.   간단하게, 몇 가지 Tag를 배울 수 있었다.…","html":"<h4><span style=\"color:#6D838C\">2. CSS </span></h4>\n<p>오늘은 <strong>CSS</strong>에 대해 배웠다.  </p>\n<p>먼저, html은 쉽게 배울 수 있지만, 가장 중요한 기초가 된다.<br>\n그리고, CSS는 HTML이 WEB의 정보에 집중할 수 있게, 디자인적 요소를 맡고 있다.  </p>\n<p>간단하게, 몇 가지 <strong>Tag</strong>를 배울 수 있었다.<br>\n<br></p>\n<hr>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">1. 폰트 색상</span></h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;font color = &quot;red&quot;&gt; 빨강 &lt;/font&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><font color = \"red\"> 빨강 </font></li>\n</ul>\n<p> <span style=\"color:#D9A493\"> <strong>※ WEB에서 무시하게 하는 방법</strong> </span>\n: <strong>&#x3C;!—</strong> <strong><strong><strong><strong>___</strong></strong></strong></strong> <strong>—></strong> 사용  </p>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">2. CSS코드로 인식 시키기</span></h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt; css코드로 인식 &lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color:#D9A493\"> <strong>HTML</strong> </span> : 모든 tag 하나하나 수정해야함<br>\n<span style=\"color:#D9A493\"> <strong>CSS</strong> </span> : 공통된 tag 하나만 수정해도 다 변경됨</li>\n</ul>\n<p>=> CSS가 효율적이다. </p>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">3. ‘a’(링크) 색상 변경</span></h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  a {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     color : red;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">4. ‘a’(링크) 밑줄</span></h6>\n<ul>\n<li>밑줄 X</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  a {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     text-decoration : none;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>밑줄 O</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  a {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     text-decoration : underline;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">5. 폰트 크기</span></h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  a {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     font-size : 45px;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">6. 정렬</span></h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  a {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     text-align : center;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p> <span style=\"color:#D9A493\"> <strong>※ 모든 링크(Black), 방문했던 페이지(Gray), 현재 페이지(Red)</strong> </span></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  .saw {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">       color : gray;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">       }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  .active {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">       color : red;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">          }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;body&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  &lt;ol&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;링크&quot; class=&quot;saw&quot; &gt; HTML &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;링크&quot; class=&quot;saw active&quot; &gt; CSS &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  &lt;/ol&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/body&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p><span style=\"color:#D9A493\"><strong>style의 .saw와 .active가 순서가 바뀌면 .active가 적용이 안됨.</strong></span><br>\n그래서, <strong>class=“saw active”</strong>를 <strong>class=“saw” id=“active”</strong>로 바꿔준다.<br>\n그리고 style의 <strong>.active</strong>를 <strong>#active</strong>로 바꿔준다면 순서에 상관 없이 적용시킬 수 있다. </p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#D9A493\"><strong>CSS코드 적용 순서</strong></span><br>\nid(#) → class(.) → Tag(a,h1,ol…)</p>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">7. 테두리</span></h6>\n<ul>\n<li>Block level element : 화면 전체를 테두리로 쓰는 것. <strong>ex) h1</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"8\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  h1 {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border-width : 5px;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border-color : black;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border-style : solid;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>inline element : 부분을 테두리로 쓰는 것. <strong>ex) a</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"9\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  h1 {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border-width : 5px;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border-color : black;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border-style : solid;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color:#D9A493\"> <strong>부분 → 전체</strong> </span> : {} 안에 <strong>display : block;</strong> 입력<br>\n<span style=\"color:#D9A493\"> <strong>전체 → 부분</strong> </span> : {} 안에 <strong>display : inline;</strong> 입력  </li>\n</ul>\n<br>  \n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color:#D9A493\"> <strong>테두리 선택자 중복 없이 줄이기</strong> </span></li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"10\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  h1 {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border : 5px black solid;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>콘텐츠와 테두리 사이 간격 조정 : {} 안에 <strong>padding : 20px;</strong> 입력  </li>\n<li>테두리와 테두리 사이 간격 조정 : {} 안에 <strong>margin : 20px;</strong> 입력  </li>\n<li>테두리 가로 길이 조정 : {} 안에 <strong>width : 100px;</strong> 입력  </li>\n<li>밑에만 테두리 지정 : {} 안에 <strong>border-bottom : 5px solid red;</strong> 입력  </li>\n</ul>\n<br>  \n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color:#D9A493\"><strong>의미 없이 디자인만을 위한 그룹 설정 tag</strong></span> </li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"11\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;div&gt;____&lt;/div&gt; : 화면 전체</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;span&gt; ____ &lt;/span&gt; : 부분</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">8. 좌우로 나누고, 테두리 설정</span></h6>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"12\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  #grid {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border : 1px black solid;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     display : grid;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     grid-template-colums : 150px 1fr; (&#39;포스트&#39;는 150px로 고정, &#39;블로그&#39;는 페이지 크기에 따라)</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  div {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     border : 5px red solid;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">     }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;body&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  &lt;div id=&quot;grid&quot;&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    &lt;div&gt; 포스트 &lt;/div&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    &lt;div&gt; 블로그 &lt;/div&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  &lt;/div&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;/body&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<h6><span style=\"color:#819BA6\">9. 미디어 쿼리</span></h6>\n<ul>\n<li>화면이 800px보다 크다면,  </li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"13\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  @media(min-width:800px) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    div {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">       display : none;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">       }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    }</span></span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>화면이 800px보다 작으면,  </li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"14\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  @media(max-width:800px) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    #grid {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">       display : block;  (800px보다 작으면, 화면 전체를 사용)</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">         }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    ol {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">       border-right : none;  (800px보다 작으면, 테두리 없앰)</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">      }</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">    }</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<span style=\"color:#D9A493\">**모든 웹페이지 공통적으로 수정하는 방법**</span>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai-dimmed grvsc-mm-tuw09S\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"15\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;style.css&quot;&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>지정한 style을 <strong>style.css</strong>로 저장하고, 그것을 불러와서 적용시키는 방법이다.<br>\n이 방법을 사용하면, 전체 페이지를 수정하지 않고 <strong>style.css</strong>만 수정하면 된다.</p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.opentutorials.org/course/1\">생활코딩</a>에서 더 자세한 내용을 확인할 수 있다. </p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .monokai-dimmed {\n    background-color: #1e1e1e;\n    color: #c5c8c6;\n  }\n  .monokai-dimmed .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n  \n  /* Monokai Dimmed */\n  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n    .grvsc-mm-tuw09S {\n      background-color: #1e1e1e;\n      color: #c5c8c6;\n    }\n    .grvsc-mm-tuw09S .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n      background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n      box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n    }\n  }\n</style>","frontmatter":{"title":"02. Blog를 위한 CSS","category":"Project","ci":"Blog","cat":"PJT","date":"2019/Nov/27","description":"[Blog] 02. Blog를 위한 CSS"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"b1f29ad8-1b2c-52ce-a0d3-e1ee968e0ca5","previousPostId":"761a1e3b-8fd7-5856-9973-3e31fdf95784","nextPostId":"e05f83a8-ea59-54c1-b9f7-50b2dfff07c6"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2151210303"]}